    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Protasius">Protasius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, rectorem <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs> beati <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/294">Sancti Donati et Sancti
                        Theodoris</orgName>, sita <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4">foras <rs
                                key="#Cities">civitate</rs> ista Lucense</placeName> […] promette a
                            <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia
                        Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        et ad successoribus tuis, finché terrà la detta chiesa seo casis et rebus ad
                        eam pertinentibus (…) di dare et perxolvere (…) ad partem ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">epischopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName> per singulos annos, in mense magio, argentum solidos
                        viginti de bonos denarios expendiviles duodecim denarios per singulos
                        solidos ratjonatos; vobis vel ad ministerialem vestro, quas in ipso <rs
                            key="#Domus">domo</rs> pro tempore abueritis (…) {da pagare de tales
                        denarios quales in die illa hic civitate Luca per caput bene fuerit
                        expendiviles. Pena: spondeo ego qui supra Protasius presbitero tibi (…), de
                        pars suprascripte ecclesie epischopatui vestro Sancti Martini, de quale anno
                        vobis suprascriptos solidos menime dederimus conponere vobis in duplum de
                        bonos denarios expendiviles. (…) et hanc promissio in suprascripto ordinem
                        in suam permaneant firmitatem quia in tali ordinem hunc scriptum <persName
                            key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petrum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> scribere rogavi. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Domus #Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"
                                ><name ref="Giselfredus">Ghiselfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wilimundus"
                            >Uuilimundus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/151">Adaldus</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Georgius">Georgius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name
                                ref="Adalbertus">Adalpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
